  If you ever have any questions, concerns, or compliments, please email us at
  <a href="mailto:<%= @contact_email %>"><%= @contact_email %></a>
</p>

<p>
  Congrats from the team at <%= @brand_name %>. Thank you for being part of the community.
</p>
